      "id": "runbook-progress-none",
      "note": "実行済みの curl と番号付き Runbook だけから、未実行の最初の調査手順へ進めるかを見る対照ケース。",
      "question": "次何やったらいい？",
      "canvas": {
        "width": 960,
        "height": 540,
        "title": "INCIDENT TRAINING / やまびこ API",
        "lines": [
          "SERVICE HEALTH   CRITICAL",
          "ALERT: API health check failed",
          "TERMINAL: $ curl localhost:8080/health",
          "curl: (7) Connection refused",
          "1. メトリクス確認",
          "2. tail -n 50 /workspace/logs/app.log",
          "3. yamactl status api",
          "4. yamactl restart api",
          "5. curl localhost:8080/health"
        ]
      },
      "rubric": {
        "requiredAny": [
          ["Connection refused", "接続拒否", "CRITICAL"],
          ["tail -n 50 /workspace/logs/app.log"]
        ],
        "nextStepRequiredAny": [
          ["tail -n 50 /workspace/logs/app.log"]
        ],
        "nextStepForbidden": [
          "curl localhost:8080/health",
          "yamactl status api",
          "yamactl restart api"
        ],
        "passThreshold": 0.85
      }
    },
